UI
Usability:
- Learnability: Should be intuitive, beshi kisu jate mukhosto na kora lage
- Efficiency: Shekhar pore use kora ta fast hocche kina
- Safety: Error kome kina and rocoverable kina. Case check kore dekha je user 
invalid input dicche kina etc. Ar vul korleo roleback kora jabe kina.

Good interface is hard to design.
- users are always right
- except when they aren't

